trans-unit.source: Provides methods that ASP.NET uses to invoke the application-preload feature in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Fornece métodos que o ASP.NET usa para invocar o recurso de pré-carregamento do aplicativo em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: Called by [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to notify ASP.NET whether an application should be preloaded.
trans-unit.target: Chamado por [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para notificar o ASP.NET se um aplicativo deve ser pré-carregados.

trans-unit.source: The unique ID of the application.
<xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> to indicate that the application should be preloaded; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>para indicar que o aplicativo deve ser pré-carregada; Caso contrário, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Calls [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] to get information that is required in order to preload an application.
trans-unit.target: Chamadas [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] para obter as informações necessárias para pré-carregar um aplicativo.

trans-unit.source: IIS calls ASP.NET through this interface, supplying a reference to an object that implements the <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil> interface.
trans-unit.target: O IIS chama ASP.NET por meio dessa interface, fornecendo uma referência a um objeto que implementa o <xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>interface.</xref:System.Web.Hosting.IApplicationPreloadUtil>

trans-unit.source: ASP.NET uses that interface later to perform a callback into IIS to get preload information for individual applications.
trans-unit.target: O ASP.NET usa essa interface posteriormente para executar um retorno de chamada no IIS para obter informações de pré-carregamento de aplicativos individuais.

trans-unit.source: The handle to an unmanaged interface in [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] that ASP.NET calls to get information.
trans-unit.target: O identificador para uma interface não gerenciado em [!INCLUDE[iisver](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] que o ASP.NET chamadas para obter informações.
